---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Contact" description="Get in touch with the CrazyQuizzes team.">
  <div class="page-badge">★ GET IN TOUCH</div>
  <h1 class="page-title">CONTACT<br><span style="color:#ff3b9a;">US</span></h1>
  <div class="page-body">
    <p>Have a quiz idea? Found a bug? Want to yell at us because your result was accurate? We're here for all of it.</p>

    <div class="contact-card">
      <h2>EMAIL US</h2>
      <p>The fastest way to reach the team:</p>
      <a class="contact-email" href="mailto:hello@crazyquizzes.com">hello@crazyquizzes.com</a>

      <h2 style="margin-top:28px;">QUIZ SUBMISSIONS</h2>
      <p>Got a quiz concept you want to pitch? Send it over with a subject line that starts with <strong>[QUIZ IDEA]</strong> and we'll take a look.</p>

      <h2>BUG REPORTS</h2>
      <p>Something broken? Tell us what happened, what browser you're on, and what you expected to see. Subject line: <strong>[BUG]</strong>.</p>
    </div>

    <p style="margin-top:28px; font-size:13px; color:#6c5a99;">We're a small team — we read every email and reply when we can. Typical response time is a few days.</p>
  </div>
</Layout>
